The patient's treatment at admission consisted in 40 mg prednisolone/d, 700 mg cyclosporine/d, 1g sodium valproate/d, 100 mg phenobarbital/d, 12,5 mg warfarin/d, prednisolone forte drops and 70 mg alendronate/week. The patient was Belgian and had been living in Brazil for the last 15 years. He did not smoke